; WEST onto s1_yard_slice's EAST exit port so the assembled floor reads as ONE
; continuous open expanse. Open cobble only — no buildings, no duplicated landmarks
; (the soft scroll-horizon east terminus, s1-cloister-yard.md §2.3).

